              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/18064897/" class="">下卷</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/luciferooo/" class=" " title="luce">luce</a>
                (草色烟光残照里)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="18064897">
